		left: 0px;
		color: #e5e1e6;
		font-size: 12px;
		pointer-events: none;
		position: absolute;
		text-align: center;
		width: 100%;
		opacity: 0.3;
		-webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(
			90deg,
			rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 5%,
			rgb(0, 0, 0) 20%,
			rgb(0, 0, 0) 80%,
			rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 95%
		);
		white-space: nowrap;
		overflow: hidden;
		z-index: 200;
	}
	main {
		min-height: 100vh;
		background: url('/grain-dark.png');
	}
	main::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		margin: 0px auto;
		left: 0px;
		top: 5vh;
		filter: brightness(0.4) sepia(1) hue-rotate(205deg) saturate(8);
		background-image: url('./assets/grid-square.svg');
		opacity: 0.2;
		-webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(70% 80% at 50% 50%, black 40%, transparent 70%);
		width: 100%;
		min-height: 90vh;
		z-index: -1;
		font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', sans-serif;
	}
</style>
